1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Trillions of neutrinos are streaming through your body right now.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,400
These ghostly particles are so small, they rarely interact with anything.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:14,000
Neutrinos are born from the sun, cosmic rays, and even nuclear reactions on Earth.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,400
Billions of them pass through every square inch of your body every second—without you even noticing.

5
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:25,200
Their weak interaction means they can travel through planets like they’re nothing.

6
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,400
Curious to learn more about these mysterious particles?

7
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:31,600
Like and follow for deeper dives into physics!
